{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"36":"Tribulations"},"section_detail":{"36":{"hadithnumber_first":3927,"hadithnumber_last":4099,"arabicnumber_first":3927,"arabicnumber_last":4099}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4021,"arabicnumber":4021,"text":"Rapporté par Bara’ bin ‘Azib : Le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) a dit : « Allah les maudira, et ceux qui maudissent les maudiront. » Il a dit : « Les habitants de la terre. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif Isnaad"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Daif Isnaad"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":36,"hadith":96}}]}